div.p:
D. Security of loans. Italians and probably some others would favor having ordinary resources of Fund stand behind repayment of loans
from special resources in event of default by borrower. Italians raised point, and Jacobsson took affirmative view. US has pointed out to French,
who agree, that such arrangement might prejudice basis for insisting that participating countries control specific lending decisions, as well as limitation of use of special resources to PC’s.
